data.description: Just like new! This neat 3 bed 2 bath is conveniently located off Goodman near shops, restaurants and the expressway! Split floor plan with a fireplace in living room. Breakfast bar in kitchen along with stainless steel dishwasher and stove. Attic area over the garage has an unfinished area that could be transformed into a bonus room, man cave. Big backyard with concrete slab for patio area. Home was built in 2019. All offers in 02/26 by 6pm
